## Context

In https://gitlab.com/gitlab-org/gitlab/-/merge_requests/52135#note_493847316 we encapsulated the event string `"issuable_vue_app:change"` in a constant, but the constant is only referenced in a single module.

## Instructions

1. Let's move this constant to `app/assets/javascripts/issuable/constants.js` (to avoid cyclical dependencies)
2. Let's update all references to `"issuable_vue_app:change"` to use this constant.

